dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents parcels for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2011. [The parcel line layer delineates parcel features such as ownership boundaries, roads, water features, easements and others that affect property ownership interests.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Delineation of Parcel Boundaries.]
